2013年7月1日，[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]宣佈舒華沙拒絕新合約離開球會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23131058 |title=Mark Schwarzer leaves Fulham after turning down new deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-01 |accessdate=2015-01-04 |archive-date=2015-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114004615/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23131058 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

