===李斯特城===
2015年1月6日，[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]第三選擇門將舒華沙免費加盟[[英超|英超]]護級球會[[李斯特城足球俱樂部|李斯特城足球俱樂部]]，合約為期至2016年夏季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/30703168 |title=Mark Schwarzer: Leicester City sign Chelsea goalkeeper |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2015-01-06 |accessdate=2015-01-07 |archive-date=2015-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107061249/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/30703168 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/leicester-city-sign-mark-schwarzer-2186274.aspx |title=Leicester City Sign Mark Schwarzer |publisher=''Leicester City F C'' |date=2015-01-06 |accessdate=2015-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403223908/http://www.lcfc.com/news/article/leicester-city-sign-mark-schwarzer-2186274.aspx |archive-date=2016-04-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。由於李斯特城的正選門將卡斯柏舒米高在2014年12月斷蹠骨而長時間養傷，而副選門將咸馬又表現不穩，今季5場失7球，因此舒華沙今次轉會，很大機會獲得他渴望的上陣時間，全力協助「狐狸」打護級戰。

===國家隊生涯===
[[File:Mark_Schwarzer-Australia.jpg|left]]
舒華沙在1993年於[[埃德蒙顿|愛民頓]]舉行的的[[1994年世界盃足球賽|1994年世界盃]]淘汰賽對陣[[加拿大國家足球隊|加拿大]]的比賽中首次為澳洲上陣。他因為正選門將[[羅拔·沙比卡|羅拔·沙比卡]]在開賽17分鐘被紅牌罰下而以替補身份入替[[米蘭·巴高積域|米蘭·巴高積域]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/Socceroo/reports/vCAN93-1.html | title=Australia vs. Canada Match Report | work=ozfootball.net | accessdate=26 February 2007 | archive-date=2013-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016235615/http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/Socceroo/reports/vCAN93-1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 在第二回合主場悉尼，他在互射十二碼階段在救出兩個關鍵十二碼，協助澳洲晉身最後一輪對陣[[阿根廷國家足球隊|阿根廷]]的淘汰賽。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/overseas-football-schwarzer-a-world-cup-hero-for-australia-1461502.html |title=Overseas Football: Schwarzer a World Cup hero for Australia |publisher=The Independent |date=16 August 1993 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |first=Rupert |last=Metcalf |archive-date=2016-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329130442/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/overseas-football-schwarzer-a-world-cup-hero-for-australia-1461502.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 舒華沙並沒有在這兩場比賽中上陣，最終澳洲以總比分1:2不敵阿根廷。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/Socceroo/1993A.html |title=Socceroo Internationals for 1993 |publisher=OzFootball.net |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330223045/http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/Socceroo/1993A.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他[[2006年世界盃足球賽|2006年世界盃足球賽]]也代表澳洲出戰[[2006年世界盃外圍賽(大洋洲區)|外圍賽]]，在淘汰賽對陣[[烏拉圭國家足球隊|烏拉圭]]。<ref name="2006WCqual">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/4435400.stm |title=Australia reach World Cup finals |publisher=BBC Sport |date=16 November 2005 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2006-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061020053607/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/4435400.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[烏拉圭國家足球隊|烏拉圭]]在[[蒙特維多|蒙特維多]]主場1:0勝出後，澳洲在2005年11月16日悉尼主場1:0回敬對手。<ref name="2006WCqual"/> 在十二碼階段，舒華沙救出對方兩個十二碼協助澳洲4:2勝出。<ref name="2006WCqual"/>

在世界盃決賽周，他為澳洲在小組賽中上陣頭兩場比賽，conceding a controversial goal against [[日本國家足球隊|日本]]，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4852706.stm |title=Australia 3-1 Japan – FIFA World Cup 2006 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=12 June 2006 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906093149/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4852706.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> and two goals against [[Brazil_national_football_team|Brazil]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853210.stm |title=Brazil 2-0 Australia – FIFA World Cup 2006 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=18 June 2006 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2007-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070604050452/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> In the third match, he was replaced by [[Željko_Kalac|Željko Kalac]], but after Kalac's disappointing performance,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853428.stm |title=Croatia 2-2 Australia – FIFA World Cup 2006 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=22 June 2006 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2006-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060821145106/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853428.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> he was reinstated for the [[Round_of_16|Round of 16]] match against [[Italy_national_football_team|Italy]].<ref name="2006ita">{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4991534.stm |title=Italy 1-0 Australia – FIFA World Cup 2006 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=26 June 2006 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802012928/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4991534.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> Although he correctly predicted the direction of the penalty kick, he was unable to save the penalty in that match, which was scored by [[Francesco_Totti|Francesco Totti]] in injury time and sent Australia out of the World Cup.<ref name="2006ita"/>

Schwarzer played in all of Australia's matches in the [[2007_AFC_Asian_Cup|2007 AFC Asian Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.soccerway.com/teams/australia/australia/156/ |title=Australia |publisher=Soccerway |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320183009/http://uk.soccerway.com/teams/australia/australia/156/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> Although he made two good saves in the opening match against [[Oman_national_football_team|Oman]], which finished as a 1–1 draw,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/asian-cup-news/cahill-averts-catastrophe-for-arnold/2007/07/08/1183833349111.html |title=Cahill averts catastrophe for Arnold |publisher=The Sydney Morning Herald |date=9 July 2007 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |first=Michael |last=Lynch |archive-date=2007-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070712120108/http://www.smh.com.au/news/asian-cup-news/cahill-averts-catastrophe-for-arnold/2007/07/08/1183833349111.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> he made an error which led to a goal in the 3–1 loss to [[Iraq_national_football_team|Iraq]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/asian-cup-news/socceroos-hang-by-a-thread/2007/07/13/1183833779791.html |title=Socceroos hang by a thread |publisher=The Sydney Morning Herald |date=14 July 2007 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |first=Michael |last=Cockerill |archive-date=2007-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070716013828/http://www.smh.com.au/news/asian-cup-news/socceroos-hang-by-a-thread/2007/07/13/1183833779791.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> In the quarter-final, he could not match Japanese goalkeeper [[Yoshikatsu_Kawaguchi|Yoshikatsu Kawaguchi]] during the penalty shootout, which saw the Socceroos get knocked out of the competition in their début at the tournament.<ref name="wrong foot">[http://www.theage.com.au/news/soccer/schwarzer-on-wrong-foot-for-first-time/2007/07/22/1185042947199.html "Schwarzer on wrong foot for first time", 25 July 2007] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/soccer/schwarzer-on-wrong-foot-for-first-time/2007/07/22/1185042947199.html |date=20160321013704 }}. Retrieved 25 July 2007</ref> Schwarzer said that the penalty shootout in the Asian Cup quarter-finals was the first penalty shoot-out in his career that he had ever lost.<ref name="wrong foot"/>

舒華沙在89分鐘時的十二碼罰球中擋下了 [[中國國家足球隊|中國]][[邵佳一|邵佳一]]的球，in Australia's 0–0 draw in the [[2010_FIFA_World_Cup_qualification_(AFC)|2010 World Cup qualifier]] in March 2008, continuing his record of stopping penalty kicks.<ref>{{cite news | last = Smithies | first = Tom | title = Schwarzer: Ball just stuck in my legs | url = http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,23438338-2883,00.html | accessdate = 28 March 2008 | work = Herald Sun | location = Australia | date = 27 March 2008 | archive-date = 2008-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080527163001/http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,23438338-2883,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
He received his second yellow card of the campaign against [[Qatar_national_football_team|Qatar]] in [[Doha|Doha]], in which Australia were 3–1 winners, leading to him being suspended for the following match against China.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://m.fifa.com/newscentre/news/newsid=802562/index.html |title=Australia thrash Qatar to top group |publisher=FIFA.com |date=14 June 2008 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150106194756/http://m.fifa.com/newscentre/news/newsid=802562/index.html |archivedate=2015年1月6日 }}</ref>

Schwarzer made several vital saves to secure Australia's [[AFC_Asian_Cup|Asian Cup Qualifier]] 2–1 comeback win over Oman in [[Muscat,_Oman|Muscat]] after conceding from his penalty save rebound.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-au/slideshow/5592/2/title/mark-schwarzers-top-five-socceroos-moments |title=Mark Schwarzer's Top Five Socceroos Moments |publisher=Goal.com |date=7 November 2013 |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305104141/http://www.goal.com/en-au/slideshow/5592/2/title/mark-schwarzers-top-five-socceroos-moments |dead-url=no }}</ref>

He was the country's first-choice keeper for all three matches of the Group Stage in the 2010 World Cup in a group composed of Australia, [[Germany_national_football_team|Germany]], [[Ghana_national_football_team|Ghana]], and [[Serbia_national_football_team|Serbia]].<ref name="FIFA record">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=94497/ |title=Mark Schwarzer |publisher=FIFA Player Statistics |accessdate=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2012-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111112907/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=94497/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> In the first match, Australia were crushed 4–0 by the Germans, but they recovered with a 1–1 draw against Ghana in the next game.<ref name="FIFA record"/> In the final match, Australia beat Serbia 2–1, thus finishing third in the group with four points, just missing out on qualification to the Round of 16 on goal difference with Ghana.<ref name="FIFA record"/>

後來，舒華沙表達了參加[[2014年世界盃|2014年世界盃]]的意願，就算他當時已41歲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/news/newsid=1697971/index.html|title=Schwarzer: Qualification drives me|date=9 September 2012|accessdate=12 November 2012|publisher=FIFA.com|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129020018/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/news/newsid=1697971/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2896/premier-league/2012/02/12/2902049/fulham-keeper-mark-schwarzer-wants-to-play-for-australia-in|title=Fulham keeper Mark Schwarzer wants to play for Australia in the 2014 World Cup|date=12 February 2012|accessdate=15 January 2013|publisher=Goal.com|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306061848/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2896/premier-league/2012/02/12/2902049/fulham-keeper-mark-schwarzer-wants-to-play-for-australia-in|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，在2013年11月5日，他宣佈決定結束國家隊球員生涯。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://theworldgame.sbs.com.au/news/1172637/Schwarzer-retires-from-Socceroos|title=Schwarzer retires from Socceroos|accessdate=6 November 2013|publisher=SBS|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105234136/http://theworldgame.sbs.com.au/news/1172637/schwarzer-retires-from-socceroos|archive-date=2013-11-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

